HC-SR04 Ultrasonic Sensor Pin Layout:
  5V -> VCC
  GND -> GND
  PA5 (GPIO_Output) -> TRIG
  PA6 (TEM3_CH1) -> ECHO

ESP-01 Wi-Fi Module:
  3V3 -> VCC
  GND -> GND
  3V3 -> CH_PD
  3V3 -> RST
  3V3 -> GPIO-2
  3V3 -> GPIO-0
  PB6 (USART1_TX) -> RXD
  PB7 (USART1_RX) -> TXD

BME-280 Combined Digital Sensor:
  PB8 (SCL) -> SCL
  PB9 (SDA) -> SDA 
  3V3 ->  VCC
  GND  -> GND
